# XTooLite

Simple SQLite tool to run simple queries over sqlite database file

#### Why XTooLite
Well it sounds like `itÂ´s too late`. cuz there exists a lot of better SQLite tools to run queries.

### Query
> [!Success] Currently only support query actions over well defined sqlite db files

#### Other actions
> [!Success] Serach and connect any sqlite db file

> [!Note] create new empty sqlite db files

## ToDo
